# Author: Duy BG VN
# ZETA AI - Processed Files Storage

# This directory stores successfully processed files
# Files are organized by user, date, and processing type

# Structure:
# processed/
# ├── documents/        # Processed documents (PDF, DOC, etc.)
# ├── images/          # Processed images (resized, optimized)
# ├── audio/           # Processed audio files (converted, enhanced)
# ├── videos/          # Processed video files (compressed, thumbnails)
# └── models/          # Processed AI model files

# Retention Policy:
# - Files are kept for 30 days by default
# - Premium users: 1 year retention
# - Enterprise users: Custom retention policy

# Backup:
# - Files are automatically backed up to cloud storage
# - Local backup retention: 7 days
# - Disaster recovery: 24 hour RPO

# Keep this directory in git but exclude actual files
